Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 24 Stanley Drive, Somerton for lease.

The property is a purpose built logistics facility comprising three separate buildings to allow specialisation of operation, product or customer. 

WAREHOUSE 1 REMAINING:

+ Total building area (warehouse 1): 10,099sqm*
+ Two level modern office: 1,387sqm*
+ High clearance warehouse: 8,712sqm*
+ Complete drive around and drive through functionality
+ 21 roller shutter doors and 4 loading docks
+ Multiple loading faces & formats
+ Large 5,069sqm* breezeway connecting three buildings
+ Excellent cross docking capabilities
+ Ample hardstand &  loading areas
+ Fully sprinklered building
+ Modern two-level partitioned corporate offices
+ Generous on-site parking
+ Direct access onto the Hume Highway

Situated in Somerton, this offering provides ease of access to and from the CBD, ports and regional Victoria. The area has attracted a range of national and international corporations including Blue Star Logistics, Mainfreight, Coles, Kraft, Qube & Boral.

*Technical Commentary Report and Rack Plan available upon request.

For futher information or to arrange an inspection of this property, please contact the marketing agents.
